{"tid":1683702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日開始罷工，我已經唔可以再扮乜事都無咁做港奴","createTime":"2019-10-30T17:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T18:40:27.000Z","uid":293326,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"59a96ddc4c7d4806282461dc3a404e341daa29c3","tid":1683702,"uid":293326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:53:07.000Z","msg":"黑警暴力愈來愈過火同嚴重<br />\n屯門今次直頭係老闆<br />\n都可以比黑警係鋪頭格硬扯出來<br />\nTg會射入民居<br />\n咁辛苦返工<br />\n捱左十幾廿年<br />\n就算有樓有鋪，面對黑警你根本無say<br />\n人地毅進仔只要有警棍<br />\n佢叫你跪係佢面前，你有樓有鋪都要跪<br />\n我咁辛苦返工做乜<br />\n我每朝返工都問自己<br />\n咁安落咁返工真係得咩？<br />\n答案係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚得</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"326e9bad6444b125e4b7280502bf86eb37717dfd","tid":1683702,"uid":293326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:54:04.000Z","msg":"每日返工都受良心責備<br />\n覺得自己無野可以做到<br />\n倒不如真係罷工<br />\n個心仲安落<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30254eb63d12e36a4d6c26507b7fd3d248594c57","tid":1683702,"uid":293326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T17:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16e29ea77dfc0c84c164146668ca44bb2c683a71","tid":1683702,"uid":18552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4bb3feabb2a034d9265a5245cdf6bc05738a72","tid":1683702,"uid":293326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T18:40:27.000Z","msg":"不如一齊罷工"}]}